qElemNumber.description: Rank number of the value, starting from 0.

qState.description: State of the value. The default state for a measure is L.

qIsEmpty.description: Is set to true, if qText and qNum are empty.

qIsTotalCell.description: Is set to true if a total is displayed in the cell.Not applicable to list objects.

qIsOtherCell.description: If set to true if the cell belongs to the group Others..Not applicable to list objects.

qIsNull.description: Is set to true if the value is Null.
